{# === 12. FAQ === #}
<twig:SectionContainer id="faq">
    {% block content %}
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        </div>
        <twig:FaqAccordion :items="[
            {question: 'Is my data safe?', answer: 'Yes. All data is encrypted at rest. IMAP credentials are protected with AES-256-GCM encryption. We never store your email content — only DMARC report metadata. Self-hosters keep everything on their own infrastructure.'},
            {question: 'How does IMAP ingestion work?', answer: 'You point your DMARC aggregate reports to a mailbox (or use our receiving address). Sendvery connects via IMAP, downloads the report attachments (XML files), parses them, and stores the structured data. The raw emails are never stored.'},
            {question: 'Can I self-host Sendvery?', answer: 'Absolutely. Sendvery is open source under AGPL-3.0. Pull the Docker image, run it on your server, and you get all features with no limits. The hosted version simply saves you the infrastructure work.'},
            {question: 'What makes Sendvery different from MXToolbox?', answer: 'MXToolbox is a great diagnostic tool. Sendvery adds continuous monitoring — we watch your DNS records 24/7 and alert you the moment something changes. Plus DMARC report parsing, AI insights in plain English, and a modern interface.'},
            {question: 'Do I need to be technical?', answer: 'No. The free DNS checker tools work for anyone — just enter your domain. For ongoing monitoring, basic familiarity with DNS is helpful, but our AI insights explain everything in plain English.'},
            {question: 'How does AI analysis work?', answer: 'Our AI analyzes your DMARC reports and DNS records to produce plain-English summaries, detect anomalies, and suggest remediation steps. Powered by Claude (Anthropic). Available as an add-on for $3.99/mo or included in the Team plan.'}
        ]" />
    {% endblock %}
</twig:SectionContainer>

{# === 13. Final CTA — Beta Signup === #}
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 via-base-100 to-accent-500/5">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Be the first to know when Sendvery launches</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base-content/60 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
            Join the beta waitlist. We'll notify you when DMARC report parsing, DNS monitoring, and AI insights are ready.
        </p>
        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-10">
            <turbo-frame id="beta-signup-form" src="{{ path('beta_signup') }}" loading="lazy">
                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <span class="loading loading-spinner loading-md text-primary"></span>
                </div>
            </turbo-frame>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{# === 14. Footer is rendered by marketing_layout.html.twig === #}

{% endblock %}
